@node Main "ColorBarr - Documentation"

                            'ColorBarr' 1.04

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  @{" ColorBarr " link play} is a game where 8 rows of coloured tiles were randomly
shuffled and it's your job to @{" move " link play} these tiles in such a way that
every row has tiles of the same colour. Arrows surrounds each game
board, and you click on them to move the tiles either up, down, left
or right. Try to complete each of the 25 game levels in the least
amount of moves.

  Have fun!

